# subscript(_:)

**Instance Subscript**

Returns an element by index.

## Declaration

```swift
subscript(index: Int) -> T { get }
```

## Overview

The index should be in the range [0, [doc://com.apple.RealityKit/documentation/RealityKit/ForceEffectParameters/physicsBodyCount]].
